reviewText: Great Documentary. Very inspiring...Made me want to sign up!
Bought this for my husband.  He and his bike buddies really liked this film.
Great documentary! Can't wait to do this ride someday!!

I have ridden RAGBRAI 3 times, once before and twice after this film was made.  It does a superb job of capturing the experience that is RAGBRAI and the state of Iowa.  It makes me want to do number 4, if it just wasn't so darned hot!!  ;-)
